# Hoist tailwindcss so that elm-tailwind-classes (which uses tailwind-resolver
# internally) and @tailwindcss/vite can resolve it at the project root level.
# tailwindcss is also declared as a direct devDependency, but the explicit
# hoist pattern ensures it is accessible to deeply-nested pnpm virtual store
# packages that don't declare it themselves.
public-hoist-pattern[]=tailwindcss
